# ===========================================
# VERCEL: Add these in Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables
# .env is for LOCAL only - Vercel uses its own env vars
# ===========================================
#
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
#   - Paste your sk_live_... or sk_test_... key
#   - NO quotes, NO extra spaces before/after
#   - From: https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
#
# SUPABASE_URL (optional - has default)
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY or SUPABASE_ANON_KEY (optional - has default)
#
# After changing env vars: Redeploy (Deployments → ⋮ → Redeploy)
